 … jīvako komārabhacco… nakulapitā gahapati… tavakaṇṇiko gahapati… pūraṇo gahapati… isidatto gahapati… sandhānosantāno 
Note { id=2, line='21', referenceLine='10', original='santāno (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' … jīvako komārabhacco… nakulapitā gahapati… tavakaṇṇiko gahapati… pūraṇo gahapati… isidatto gahapati… sandhāno '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='sandhāno'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='santāno'}}
 gahapati… vicayovijayo 
Note { id=3, line='30', referenceLine='10', original='vijayo (sī. syā. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' gahapati… vicayo '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='vicayo'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā. pī.', text='vijayo'}}
vajjiyamahito (sī. syā. pī.)sādatto (syā.)upāsako tathāgate niṭṭhaṅgato amataddaso amataṃ sacchikatvā iriyati. Katamehi chahi? Buddhe aveccappasādena, dhamme aveccappasādena, saṅghe aveccappasādena, ariyena sīlena, ariyena ñāṇena, ariyāya vimuttiyā. Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato sāraggo upāsako tathāgate niṭṭhaṅgato amataddaso amataṃ sacchikatvā iriyatī’’ti. Tevīsatimaṃ.
